[I] Library for creating GUIs for games and 3D applications

[T] MyGUI is a cross-platform library for creating graphical user interfaces
[T] (GUIs) for games and 3D applications.

[U] http://mygui.info/

[A] The mygui Project
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

